{"tid":375010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記得夜晚唔好出街","createTime":"2017-08-26T07:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T08:40:29.000Z","uid":139598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba60b553ce72c5029349f64f5419e28afd7b22dc","tid":375010,"uid":139598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">真人真事唔好笑我</span><br />\n話說琴日我大約7 00係QE探病，日日都有去都冇咩奇怪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚去，然後突然有個婆婆問我點去某座，我就話我都係去個到，我帶你去啦！<br />\n然後一直都平排行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到一齊入門口，我去㩒升降機，一轉返過去佢就唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重點係冇開門聲，係消失左</span><br />\n因為自動門係有聲，但係就乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家仲驚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家分享下自己嘅恐怕經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8b250613c8249705b74c1e955a99b2344d9a0d","tid":375010,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"小弟見識淺，乜自動門開門有聲架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9f9e7b528711b7905601942d2730d2eedf32d5","tid":375010,"uid":74851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟見識淺，乜自動門開門有聲架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見識都幾淺"},{"pid":"49aed18e04ef505efbe04db2e0755f0d503befd6","tid":375010,"uid":139598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟見識淺，乜自動門開門有聲架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫院個D點都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9649fdedebba99f67a9ff926d21e4fcc3dfbbc96","tid":375010,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"身已上<br />\n而係係個呀婆代樓豬出po"},{"pid":"66be7ec7d214a5ef6a906e95d4db2545ccfde006","tid":375010,"uid":139598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身已上<br />\n而係係個呀婆代樓豬出po</blockquote><br />\n呀婆感in上連登？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c85c9523c3cccffb8e967df6cc885e1342a8c4","tid":375010,"uid":14214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"其實呀婆想行樓梯"}]}